public class LostPromotions
extends DynamoServlet

Determines which promotions that were applied at the start of the return are no longer applied based on the current state of the return.

input params

returnRequest
(required)the return request to be checked.
oparams
output
rendered once once with the promotions that no longer apply
empty
rendered once once when there are no promotions that no longer apply
